flowchart TD
    R1[POI submitted by Saler] --> R2[Set PendingReview]
    R2 --> R3{Duplicate detected?}
    R3 -- Yes --> R4[Create duplicate report + warning]
    R3 -- No --> R5[Wait admin review]
    R5 --> R6{Admin action}
    R6 -- Approve --> R7[Visible to App users]
    R6 -- Reject --> R8[Store rejection reason]
    R6 -- Lock --> R9[Saler cannot edit]
    R7 --> R10{Audio available?}
    R10 -- Yes --> R11[Play file]
    R10 -- No --> R12[TTS fallback]
